starvationevasion.client.MegaMawile.ai.brain

Enum AiState

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AiState>
      • starvationevasion.client.MegaMawile.ai.brain.AiState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AiState>

    public enum AiState
extends java.lang.Enum<AiState>
    An enumeration of AI states which, depending on their combination, influence
    AI behavior. Each state should have an "inverse" which allows the Ai to alter its
    behavior if a previous state led to negative consequences.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      COLLABORATING

      CONSERVATIVE
      AI will tend to favor "conservative" policies, and spend less on them.
      DECIDING
      AI is in the middle of a decision.
      ISOLATING
      AI will collaborate less.
      LIBERAL
      AI will tend to favor "liberal" policies, and put more money towards them.
      WAITING
      AI has completed its decisions for this round.
